# Ilmla Bot — Ishga Tushirish Qo'llanmasi

## 1. O'rnatish

```bash
# Python 3.10+ kerak
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate        # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## 2. Bot tokenini olish

1. Telegramda @BotFather ga yozing
2. /newbot buyrug'ini yuboring
3. Bot nomini kiriting: `Ilmla Bot`
4. Username kiriting: `ilmla_edu_bot` (yoki boshqa)
5. Olingan tokenni `bot.py` dagi `BOT_TOKEN` ga qo'ying

## 3. Owner ID ni aniqlash

@userinfobot ga /start yuboring — u sizning ID raqamingizni ko'rsatadi.
Uni `bot.py` dagi `OWNER_ID` ga qo'ying.

## 4. Admin ma'lumotlarini yangilash

`bot.py` faylida `ADMIN_INFO` qismini o'zgartiring:

```python
ADMIN_INFO = {
    "name":     "Ismingiz",
    "phone":    "+998 XX XXX XX XX",
    "telegram": "@username",
    "address":  "Manzil",
    "hours":    "Ish vaqti",
}
```

## 5. Botni ishga tushirish

```bash
python bot.py
```

## 6. Serverda doimiy ishlatish (Linux)

```bash
# systemd service yaratish
sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/ilmla_bot.service
```

```ini
[Unit]
Description=Ilmla Telegram Bot
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=ubuntu
WorkingDirectory=/home/ubuntu/ilmla_bot
ExecStart=/home/ubuntu/ilmla_bot/venv/bin/python bot.py
Restart=always
RestartSec=10

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

```bash
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable ilmla_bot
sudo systemctl start ilmla_bot
sudo systemctl status ilmla_bot
```

## 7. FAQ qo'shish

Admin sifatida botga:
```
/addfaq Savol matni | Javob matni
```

## 8. Loglarni ko'rish

```bash
tail -f ilmla_bot.log
```

---

## Bot imkoniyatlari

| Foydalanuvchi | Admin |
|---|---|
| Ro'yxatdan o'tish | Statistika |
| Kurslar haqida | O'quvchilar ro'yxati |
| FAQ | Broadcast xabar |
| Admin bilan bog'lanish | FAQ boshqaruv |

## Ikkinchi bot bilan ulash (notifications)

Agar xabarlarni boshqa botga yubormoqchi bo'lsangiz, `bot.py`ning oxirida:

```python
SECOND_BOT_TOKEN = "IKKINCHI_BOT_TOKENI"
SECOND_BOT_CHAT_ID = -100xxxxxxxxx  # kanal yoki guruh ID

# bot.send_message() o'rniga:
import httpx
httpx.post(
    f"https://api.telegram.org/bot{SECOND_BOT_TOKEN}/sendMessage",
    json={"chat_id": SECOND_BOT_CHAT_ID, "text": "...", "parse_mode": "Markdown"}
)
```